    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine, showroom condition. This meticulously maintained example boasts a flawless exterior and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Rigorously inspected by our senior technicians to ensure mechanical perfection, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. For the buyer seeking a no-compromise driving experience, this is the definitive choice. Delivered with a comprehensive service history and our uncompromising seal of quality.",
      "price": 47500.0,
